query:
SELECT a.id, a.studentId, s.name as studentName, a.mainGoal, a.occupation, a.version 
FROM anamneses a 
JOIN students s ON a.studentId = s.id 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Paulo%' OR s.name LIKE '%Tescaro%'
ORDER BY a.id DESC
LIMIT 5;
